title: Teen Survives Nearly 100-Foot Fall at North Rim of Grand Canyon
description: Authorities said it took emergency crews two hours to rescue Wyatt Kauffman after he slipped on a cliff Tuesday.

title: Child Influencers in Illinois Will Be Able to Sue if Earnings Aren’t Set Aside

title: 4 People Dead After Explosion Destroys 3 Structures in Pennsylvania
